Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on Foundation…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.21,0:00:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你带了个东西 色彩校正镜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've brought you something. Color-correction 'hesives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就能看到红绿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you can see red and green.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们知道我的与众不同 那会是我在世上的最后一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they ever learn how different I am, it'll be my last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射死六只 这一定能让黄昏兄弟印象深刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Six kills. Brother Dusk will be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这些扔进树丛 我射死了三只\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Throw these in the bushes. I killed three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉想让我们帮她取得战舰的掌控权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phara wants us to help her take control of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无敌战舰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Invictus?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个摧毁世界的杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A world-killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些老式飞船 需要具备强大处理能力的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These older ships needed something with massive processing power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来为跃迁提供导航\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to navigate their jumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不得不与飞船直接相连\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They had to be hardwired directly into the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做手术可以直接连接吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could someone jack in without the surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等于判了死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would be a death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（改编自艾萨克阿西莫夫的小说）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若问历史学家 “人类最伟大的发明是什么 ”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ask a historian, "What was mankind's greatest invention?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火 车轮 刀剑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire? The wheel? The sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会说是历史本身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would argue it's history itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史不是一种事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}History isn't fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是一种故事 精心策划和塑造的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's narrative, one carefully curated and shaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在合适的人笔下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Under the pen strokes of the right scribe,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶棍能变成英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a villain becomes a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谎言能变成真理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a lie becomes the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-爸爸 -怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Daddy? -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们来自哪里  -川陀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Where did we come from? -Trantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 在那之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类在哪里诞生 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did people come from in the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有许多不同的理论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are lots of different theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分认为人类最初 居住在一个单一星球系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most of them say that humans originally inhabited a single planetary system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至不知道是哪一个星球 天狼星 南门二星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we don't even know which. Sirius, Alpha Centauri…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人认为我们来自一个叫地球的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people think that we came from some place called Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here. Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.78,0:02:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们所知的一切人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, everyone we know about,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都来自同一个地方吗  包括安纳克里昂人和狄斯比斯人 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they also came from the same place? Anacreons and Thespins too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也包括安纳克里昂人和狄斯比斯人 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreons and Thespins too, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他们为什么恨我们 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then how can they hate us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类是复杂的 塞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Being human is complicated, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有共同的起源 也有一些相同的传说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We share a common origin and some of the same myths.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们被大脑所控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're governed by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大脑赋予我们一切理性思考的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In here is all the capacity for rational thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但与此同时 感性情感也存在于大脑中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's sharing skull space with our emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时感性的声音大过理性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And sometimes emotions shout louder than logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人的感性令他们坚信 帝国对他们不公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And somebody's emotions got real insistent that the Empire were doing them wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们炸毁星桥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So they blew up the Star Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴力是无能者最后的庇护所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Violence is the last refuge of the incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们和我们完全不同 对吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, they're not like us at all then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小脑袋里感性的声音也很大呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It gets loud up inside here too, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞 问题是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's the thing, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星桥被炸毁时 数百万人死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Millions of people died when that Star Bridge came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后大帝又杀死了数百万的 安纳克里昂人和狄斯比斯人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the Empire killed many millions more on Anacreon and Thespis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到底谁赢了呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And who won?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没有人赢  -没有人赢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nobody? -Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那时我们明白了 帝国的灭亡和文明的丧失不可避免\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's how we know that the fall is bound to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过往的行为是预测未来表现的最佳指标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Past behavior is the best predictor of future performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛哈定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor Hardin…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在跃迁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lewis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯 你在哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lewis, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端点星 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跃迁回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We jumped back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lewis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心愿护送我们回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wished us home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端点星指挥部 我是塞佛哈定 在帝国无敌战舰上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus Control, this is Salvor Hardin, on board the imperial warship Invictus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否收到 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端点星指挥部 是否收到 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus Control, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塞佛哈定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Salvor Hardin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能听见吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can anybody hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塞佛哈定 呼叫狄斯比斯骑兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Salvor Hardin calling the Thespin lancers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无敌战舰跃迁了 你们的飞船被带入我们的量子尾波\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Invictus jumped and we've dragged your ships into our quantum wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在环绕端点星轨道飞行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're in orbit around Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能听见 我不知道 如何阻止飞船再次跃迁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can hear me, I have no idea how to stop this ship from jumping again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许一小时后会跃迁 也许是几天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It could be an hour from now. It could be days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我被困在这里了 除非…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I figure I'm stuck here, unless…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乞丐号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Beggar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.95,0:09:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么回家 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我解释一下详细路线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take me through your route.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个走廊通向哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where does this corridor go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下灌溉系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The underground irrigation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那上方有一条路可以穿过宫殿废墟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there's a path above it you could take through the old palace ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后你会来到仆从的出口 就在宫殿大门附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You end up at the servants' exit, right next to the palace gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果我从这里出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, if I could exit here…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超循环站就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hyperloop station's just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大门安检需要扫描DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gate security has DNA scanners.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要信号消除器 隐藏我的纳米机器人 这样他们就无法追踪我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll need the signal damper. For my nanobots. So they can't track me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我可以给你弄一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I can get you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't wanna die in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能保证一切会顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't promise it'll all go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能保证我不会是出错的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I can promise is I won't be the part that goes wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了 黄昏兄弟在…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to go. Brother Dusk is--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里昂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleon--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真希望你不叫这个名字 拥有只属于你的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish you had another name. One that was just yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你可以为我起一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tomorrow you can give me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把信号消除器带给我 我们在另一边见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get me that signal damper, and I'll see you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 黄昏兄弟 我刚才…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My apologies, Brother Dusk. I was--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 年轻人的时间概念和我不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand. Time flows differently when you're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你说一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to share something with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 这是我的工作地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is my workplace, as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏最重要的任务之一 是以画面记录我们的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The signature task of Dusk is to record our visual history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机器人战争的结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The end of the Robot Wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金马之叛乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Golden Horse Rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当我们王朝来到了变革点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Each moment an inflection point for our dynasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星系的命运似乎都岌岌可危\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the fate of the galaxy seemed to be hanging in the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这一时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As it did here…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为蛮族的野蛮之举而惩罚他们的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when I chastened the barbarian worlds for their acts of savagery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作画的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even while I was painting it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心里想着我们作为历史的谱写者 将如何被描述\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was conscious of how we, as its authors, would be represented.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪明的艺术家以作品表达论点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A clever artist provides commentary with his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是色彩选择这么简单的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even something as simple as a choice of color
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能传递隐含的意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can convey a hidden meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时历史性的时刻并不明显\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And sometimes the moment's not so obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时它会被我们忽略\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes it slips past us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直没有意识到它 直到那一刻过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you don't even realize it until it is past,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你第一次出现在墙上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until your debut on the wall is upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将你画进了我们的画谱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've painted you into our legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的狩猎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到你击中的那三只基力猛龙了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you see the three ghillie raptors you shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾梦想有一天 我能做些丰功伟绩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've dreamed of one day doing something,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以让我有资格出现在这壁画里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}anything, worthy enough to be included in this mural.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道为何这一小事会…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know why this small feat is…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到很荣幸 谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm honored. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本就知道你具有克里昂一世的伟大品质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew you had the greatness of Cleon I in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在我们狩猎期间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But during our hunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才意识到你还有其他品质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I realized there was something else inside you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了 你可以独自回顾 属于你的光辉时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll leave you to reflect on your own glorious moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欣赏微妙细腻的笔触吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Appreciate the subtleties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们选择让后代知道什么 对他们隐瞒什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What we choose to tell our children and what we censor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突出什么 简化什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What we illuminate and what we gloss over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史是一种不断做加减法的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}History as an act of addition and subtraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:15:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝 请你去元帝塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire, you're needed in the Principium Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我有事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't. I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是黄昏兄弟的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Dusk insists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身体有恙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm indisposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一分钟 我会去的 只需一分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need a minute alone, and I'll come along. One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 我也是大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am also Empire, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们都服侍帝国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we both serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了东西 我需要回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I forgot something. I need to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁入口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lock down the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许任何人进出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't let anyone in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有条路可以穿过宫殿废墟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a path you can take through the palace ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后你会来到仆从的出口 就在宫殿大门附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You end up at the servants' exit, right next to the palace gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路通向地下灌溉系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This route takes you to the underground irrigation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超循环站就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hyperloop station's just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散开来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spread out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 水循环即将开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warning. Water cycling imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 水循环即将开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warning. Water cycling imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊 这个跳跃的距离也太远了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Four moons, that's a long jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乞丐号 快给我醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beggar, wake the hell up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎上船 哈定船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome aboard, Captain Hardin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是帝国护身环 能换你的外套吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an imperial aura. For your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能告诉我怎么去33层的德司尼安区吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you tell me how to get to the Desnian Sector on level 33?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐钴线向下 然后转乘埃利环线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take the Cobalt Line down, then transfer to Ery Loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向核心区走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You wanna head inner core.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乞丐号 开启连接端点星的频道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beggar, open a channel to Terminus Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯频道已开启\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Communications channel open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端点星指挥部 我是塞佛哈定 请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terminus Control, this is Salvor Hardin. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乞丐号 扫描所有波幅 寻找任何可连接的通讯点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beggar, scan all frequencies. Find me anyone on comms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫描中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scanning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未发现端点星地表上 存在任何运行的通讯站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No active comms detected on the surface of Terminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You found someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 异常碎屑 可能位于撞击轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Caution. Anomalous debris on potential intercept trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险级别低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Threat level low.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么鬼东西 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.35,0:22:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 异常碎屑 确认位于撞击轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alert. Anomalous debris on confirmed intercept trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险级别中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Threat level moderate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要火炮 火炮在哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need guns. Where are the guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乞丐号 说明火炮位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beggar, show me the guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告 异常碎屑即将撞击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warning. Anomalous debris object impact imminent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险级别极高 警告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Threat level severe. Warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁定目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Target locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.91,0:22:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 是你吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Babe? Babe, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.04,0:22:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨果 是你吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hugo, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的计划成功了 塞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our plan worked, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么从星带过来的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you get here from the Belt?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要靠运气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luck, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我联络上狄斯比斯指挥部 我搭上了其中一艘骑兵飞船的副驾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made contact with Thespin Command. I rode shotgun on one of the lancers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:23:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现无敌战舰即将跃迁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then I could see the Invictus was about to jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我拿了一个麻醉棍 让自己晕了过去 以进行跃迁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I grabbed a sedation stick and knocked myself out for the jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提醒其他人也这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warned the rest of my people to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来就听见你美妙的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I woke up to the dulcet tones of your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.83,0:23:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不明白为什么你这么快醒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I don't understand how you woke up so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有真的睡过去 就和穹窿一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never went to sleep. It's like the Vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法解释原因 但跃迁对我没有影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't explain how or why, but the jump just didn't affect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.97,0:23:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你带我们回到端点星了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you got us back to Terminus?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是路易斯的功劳 他为了送我们回家牺牲了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that was Lewis. He died to get us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地没有回应 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the Foundation's not responding?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何人回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one is,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连法拉留下的安纳克里昂人都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not even the Anacreons Phara left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.86,0:23:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空域的作用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the null field.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.53,0:23:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到 雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can feel it, Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它变得更大 更响了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's… even bigger. It's… louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.33,0:23:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像在慢慢包裹整个星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like it's enveloped the whole planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:23:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须阻止它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:23:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.88,0:24:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他们都死了呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if they're all dead down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我们直接离开 就现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if we just left? Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.76,0:24:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以去红廊避难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll make a run for the Red Corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.18,0:24:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以带你看艾琳娜四号星 长庚星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll show you Irina Four, I'll show you Hesperus--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能这么做 雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't, Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.52,0:24:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这场危机并没有解决方案呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if there is no solution to this crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.10,0:24:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果谢顿的预测是错的呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if Seldon got it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.28,0:24:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须坚持到最后 雨果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to see this through, Hugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.08,0:24:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须挽回局面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.88,0:24:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我怎么做 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.72,0:24:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无敌战舰会再次跃迁 除非你的人能够关闭它的驱动器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Invictus is gonna jump again unless your people can disable its drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.10,0:24:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让它跃迁 让它带走法拉 我们再也不用见它了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then let it jump. Let it take Phara. It'll be out of our lives forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.64,0:24:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.14,0:24:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地需要这艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Foundation needs that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.40,0:25:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们终结危机的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the way we end the crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.57,0:25:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我无法告诉你如何… -我只是有种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I can't tell you how… -I just have a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.49,0:25:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过你对我坚信不疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you have absolute faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.38,0:25:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的信念动摇了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.84,0:25:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在改变主意 我是不是有点过分 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be kind of a dick if I changed my mind now, wouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.86,0:25:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在目的地见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.04,0:25:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.33,0:25:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.40,0:26:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你人生的每一分 每一秒 都在别人的注视下度过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've lived every moment of your life with people watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.73,0:26:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疤痕区不是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Scar's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.36,0:26:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以在那里混入人群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can lose yourself in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.78,0:26:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于帝国而言 疤痕区代表着失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For Empire, the Scar represents a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.74,0:26:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于川陀的其他人来说 它是一次机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the rest of Trantor, it represents an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.12,0:26:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数百年来的第一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the first time in centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.79,0:26:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以抬头看见真的云朵和星辰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can look up and see real clouds, real stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.21,0:26:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是为了让我们安于现状的 服务器运行模拟天空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not a simulation run by servers designed to keep us complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.06,0:27:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居住在第33层的德司尼安区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I live on level 33, in the Desnian Sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.49,0:27:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老特尔夏做的风味马尔卡饼 是整个星球最美味的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old Tertia makes the best spiced malkas on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.24,0:27:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我称之为家的走廊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the corridor I take home.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.83,0:27:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的宫殿是两个天地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nothing like your palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.29,0:27:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吵闹喧嚣 熙熙攘攘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's chaotic. It's crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.85,0:27:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里是鲜活的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.06,0:27:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它正等着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.25,0:28:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再等了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.82,0:28:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有戴护身环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not wearing your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.07,0:28:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用它换了这件外套 以免别人认出我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I traded it for this, so I wouldn't be recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.12,0:28:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换外套这招挺聪明的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The jacket's smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.29,0:28:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们可以烧了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now we can burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.89,0:29:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得移除我的纳米机器人 以防他们在追踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to get my nanobots removed in case they're tracking me. I…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.73,0:29:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许根本不该留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I probably shouldn't even stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.48,0:29:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我有信号消除器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay. I got the signal damper.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.57,0:29:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可以隐藏你的踪迹 直到我们…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That'll cover you until we can arrange to…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.20,0:29:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.58,0:29:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最难的部分已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hardest part's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.00,0:29:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃离了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.80,0:29:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来到这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.93,0:29:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 说真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, truthfully…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.89,0:29:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上的味道仍然很难闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you still smell terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.44,0:29:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如你洗个澡吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.97,0:30:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 我在想给自己起个新名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, I was thinking about a new name for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.14,0:30:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿祖拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Azura?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.82,0:30:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是用来做什么的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.89,0:31:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛说引擎室在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to Salvor, the engine room is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.44,0:31:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有大约33个小时来关闭跃迁驱动器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got about thirty-three hours to disable the jumpdrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.57,0:32:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里发生了什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.07,0:32:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个漫长而可怕的故事 没有人活下来讲述它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A long and terrible story that no one's alive to tell…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.53,0:32:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂人在哪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreons, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.54,0:32:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥那边 塞佛把他们绑在那里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bridge. Salvor has them tied up in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.46,0:32:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.06,0:32:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位智者曾说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A wise man once said,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.98,0:32:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“没有历史的民族就如无根的树”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"A people without history is like a tree without roots."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.94,0:32:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位智者的历史缺失了什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's missing from the wise man's history?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.61,0:32:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从何时开始 故事代替了事实 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When did story replace record?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.12,0:32:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当所有事实都不再可信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When all the facts fall short of believability,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.75,0:32:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想反而有一种令人安心的真实感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}fantasy feels reassuringly solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.79,0:32:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而由于这是我的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And since this is my history,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.59,0:33:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以决定删减哪一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get to decide which parts have been subtracted,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.55,0:33:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增添哪一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which have been added.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.01,0:34:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jord?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.79,0:35:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom? Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.29,0:35:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…醒醒 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom. Mom, wake up, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.46,0:35:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…醒醒 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom. Mom, wake up, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.69,0:36:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解它吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you make anything of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.93,0:36:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我自己破解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine. I'll figure it out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.71,0:37:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松开拳头 塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open your fists, Salvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.84,0:37:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松开拳头 塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open your fists, Salvor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.34,0:37:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.61,0:37:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能理解它吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you make anything of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.44,0:37:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛 如果你是计划的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor, if you were part of the Plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.15,0:37:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我会更容易相信这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would make it a lot easier for me to believe in all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.92,0:37:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long did it take you…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.76,0:37:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激活元光体 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to trigger the Prime Radiant?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.88,0:37:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第二次尝试时成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got it on the second try.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.40,0:38:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史是终极武器 因为它能驾驭时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}History is the ultimate weapon, because it harnesses time itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.78,0:38:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地利用时间 过去就能改变现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Used correctly, the past can alter the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.16,0:38:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哪种发明能够做到这点 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What other invention can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.88,0:39:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.26,0:39:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.81,0:39:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我还以为再也见不到你了 -我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I thought I'd never see you again. -Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.28,0:39:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空域停止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The null field, it's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.00,0:39:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.85,0:40:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是门吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that a door?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.02,0:40:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.56,0:40:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在怎么办 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.52,0:40:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是结束的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now is where it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.74,0:40:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到猎手了吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you find the Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.83,0:40:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们搜寻了整艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We searched the entire ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.54,0:40:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有她的踪迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No sign of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.79,0:40:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.13,0:40:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们尽快赶到端点星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we get down to Terminus as fast as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.63,0:40:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑曜岩号 开启与长石砂岩号 和片麻岩号的通讯频道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Obsidian, open a channel to Arkose and Gneiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.55,0:40:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通讯频道已开启\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Communications channel open.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.81,0:40:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是狄斯比斯指挥部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Thespin Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.43,0:40:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有骑兵立即前往星球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want all lancers planet-side immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.60,0:40:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞船由你们中的谁指挥 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which one of you is this ship slave to?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.07,0:41:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让飞船听命于法拉柯恩 否则你也会死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slave this ship to Phara Keaen, or you die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.03,0:41:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长石砂岩号 启动规程 飞船转移 法拉柯恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Arkose, invoke protocol. Ship transfer, Phara Keaen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.09,0:41:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心率增加\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heart rate's rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.14,0:41:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果达到120次 那么机器人会进入紧急模式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it gets to 120, then the bots go into crisis mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.35,0:41:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会增加抑制剂量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll increase the inhibitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.11,0:41:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脉搏渐渐平稳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pulse is stabilizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.15,0:41:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始传输吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Start the transfer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.98,0:42:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正将你的纳米机器人传输至我的血液\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're transferring your nanobots into my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.45,0:42:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你想要的 对吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what you wanted, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.57,0:42:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移除它们 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To have them removed?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.16,0:42:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.37,0:42:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明的克隆人 显而易见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A Dawn clone, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.50,0:42:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外表上与你一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Superficially identical to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.42,0:42:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是如何…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.29,0:42:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这里 而不是漂浮在水族箱里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here? Instead of floating in an aquarium?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.97,0:42:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的人成功将克里昂一世的部分DNA 从宫殿中偷出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our people managed to smuggle some of Cleon I's DNA out of the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.30,0:42:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这一天 我们已经努力了数十年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been working towards this day for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.31,0:42:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出乎我们的意料 我们原计划明天才帮你逃出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You surprised us. We'd planned to have you escape tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.94,0:43:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿祖拉在哪里 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Azura?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.12,0:43:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是陷阱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was all a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.33,0:43:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能这样对我 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could you do this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.08,0:43:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.21,0:43:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这关乎星系的其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is about the rest of the galaxy,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.42,0:43:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有被帝国压迫的星球和人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all the planets and people who've been crushed under the Empire's heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.63,0:43:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是他的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.21,0:43:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在这种环境下长大的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's how he was raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.18,0:43:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 他和他的兄弟们总是听人们说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He and his brothers have always been told
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.51,0:43:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是不会灭的明光 永不断裂的锁链\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they are the light that never dims, an unbroken chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.48,0:43:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们那小天地的宫墙隔离了残酷的现实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reality just doesn't penetrate their little terrarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.48,0:43:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你要如何忍受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how you're gonna stomach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.73,0:43:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会有事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.73,0:43:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经练习扮演这个角色太久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been practicing my role long enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.82,0:43:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚在成长的小暴君\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the cloistered little tyrant in the making…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.53,0:44:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上笼罩着一种微弱的 自怜又自负的高冷气质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}projecting that subtle air of self-pitying, arrogant indifference.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.71,0:44:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习 你在说什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Practicing? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.26,0:44:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“练习 你在说什么 ”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Practicing? What are you talking about?"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.84,0:44:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的替身 黎明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm your understudy, Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.76,0:44:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我该登上舞台了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now it's time for me to take center stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.85,0:44:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会回到宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to go back to the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.14,0:44:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I'm gonna be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.15,0:44:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会杀了你 他们知道我不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll just kill you then. They know I'm different.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.15,0:44:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 可是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.40,0:44:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与你不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.28,0:44:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并非色盲 我不是左撇子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not color-blind. I'm not left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.66,0:44:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在基因上 我与克里昂一世一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm genetically identical to Cleon I.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.96,0:44:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以证明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I can prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.42,0:44:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.42,0:44:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能你与一世一模一样而我却不是 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can you be identical to the first, and I'm not?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.51,0:44:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术术语是“磁性纳米粒子转染”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Magnetic nanoparticle transfection" is the technical term.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.47,0:44:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体情况太过复杂 我也不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all a little over my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.39,0:45:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是简单说来 在克隆你之后 他们修改了你的DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but, basically, they altered your DNA after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.14,0:45:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如我说的 在你我出生之前 这一切都已计划好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like I said, this has been planned since before you or I took our first breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.73,0:45:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的人明白必须让你离开宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our people knew they had to get you out of the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.52,0:45:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们不能直接绑走你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but they couldn't just take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.82,0:45:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样太危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would've been too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.94,0:45:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们必须让你自己选择离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They had to make it so you'd choose to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.11,0:45:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要一个逃走的动机 还有比生存更好的动机吗 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You needed a motive to run. And what better motive than survival?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.08,0:45:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝 是我们让你变得不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're the ones who made you different, Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.04,0:45:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从某种意义而言 你其实很幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a certain way, you're lucky too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.21,0:45:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脉相承的王朝是人类的耻辱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Genetic Dynasty's an affront to humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.55,0:45:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你已不是其中的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you're no longer part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.64,0:45:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从来都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.56,0:45:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传输完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The transfer's complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.50,0:46:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头到尾 你没有任何选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had no choice in any of this…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.05,0:46:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们仍然感谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but thank you just the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.68,0:46:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扶他起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.77,0:46:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要对我做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you gonna do to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.52,0:46:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢 克里昂 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think, Cleon?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.18,0:47:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿祖拉…这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Azura. Azura, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.95,0:47:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.33,0:47:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏兄弟 我真感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Dusk! I am so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.62,0:47:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底审查所有死者的记忆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want a full memory audit of all the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.08,0:47:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.34,0:47:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩 是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The girl. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.14,0:47:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演技令人赞叹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quite a performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.89,0:47:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为观众欣赏这场表演 很荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a pleasure to observe it,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.93,0:47:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只能蒙骗年轻人和傻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tailored though it was to the young and foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.57,0:48:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会认为 我们会任由这个无人机离开宫殿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't really think we'd let this drone leave the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.87,0:48:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不通知我们吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without alerting us, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.87,0:48:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 我们一路跟随你们 令人激动的旅程 回到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We followed your whole enticing travelogue home, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.05,0:48:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放他走 从而跟着他找到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You let him get away so he would lead you to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.01,0:48:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捆缚她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shroud her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.07,0:48:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经得到你想要的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got what you wanted then.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.91,0:48:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远别以为你理解我想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never presume to understand what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.29,0:49:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愚蠢 天真 易受骗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are stupid, naive, gullible.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.88,0:49:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在你这个年纪也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So was I at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.80,0:49:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是可以原谅的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And these things are forgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.55,0:49:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的不同之处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the matter of your… difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.01,0:49:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题则复杂得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's rather more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.56,0:49:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你一定也听到他们的话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you must've heard them.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.56,0:49:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受害者 我们都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a victim. We all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.31,0:49:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.77,0:49:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让你变成我们脆弱的象征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that makes you the embodiment of our vulnerability,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.24,0:49:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个令人不快的标识 提醒着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}an ugly reminder of the knife-edge
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.95,0:49:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脉相承的王朝之根基如此脆弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}upon which our Genetic Dynasty is balanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.24,0:49:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有何理由会想再看到你的脸 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By what logic would we want to look on your face ever again?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.08,0:49:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My face?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.96,0:49:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脸就是你的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My face is your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.55,0:49:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管逻辑 试着换位思考一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forget logic. Try empathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.35,0:49:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.23,0:50:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是你说了算 而取决于白昼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surely it's not up to you. It's up to Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.73,0:50:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.36,0:50:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白昼兄弟很快将回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brother Day will be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.78,0:50:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以向他求情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can plead your case to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.57,0:50:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他在经历了少女星的事之后 应该是心烦意乱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I doubt his experience on the Maiden has made him serene.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.92,0:50:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守卫者 你安全返回了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Warden, you made it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.42,0:50:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人离我远点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep your distance, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.09,0:50:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家都醒了 已经结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But everyone's waking up. It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.35,0:50:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.93,0:50:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞佛 等等 别过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Salvor, wait. Don't go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.52,0:50:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须这么做 妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.64,0:50:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去 止步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will not! Step away.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.06,0:50:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过这不是陷阱 你不知道这是什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said this wasn't a trick, that you didn't know what this was.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.36,0:50:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们确实不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.44,0:50:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你的女儿却让它停止了 你要如何解释 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet your daughter has tamed it. How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.22,0:51:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 塞 我试图说服他们别着陆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, Sal. I tried to talk 'em out of landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.01,0:51:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是合理的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, this makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.93,0:52:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该在这里 所有事件汇合为一场危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is where I'm supposed to be. Everything converging in a single crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.44,0:52:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的猎手在哪 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is our Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.61,0:52:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她失去了对无敌战舰的控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She lost control of the Invictus.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.28,0:52:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们殉道 摧毁川陀的计划已经失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your plans for martyrdom, for Trantor, they're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.11,0:52:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗文 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rowan?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.20,0:52:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维伊尔德诸神已经背弃我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Weald Gods have forsaken us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.23,0:52:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 真该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, hammered shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.41,0:53:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这画面真美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, isn't this a pretty picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.84,0:53:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新旧敌人齐聚一堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enemies old and new, conveniently gathered in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.26,0:53:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下武器 给他松绑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drop your weapons and unbind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.98,0:53:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 守卫者 别想着抛你那枚硬币\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you, Warden, don't even think about flashing that coin of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.32,0:53:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉 很高兴你还活着 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm glad you're alive, Phara, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.66,0:53:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你也听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.74,0:53:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最不想听的就是你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Last thing I'm interested in hearing is more words from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.24,0:53:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉 拜托了 跃迁会导致精神错乱 你的思维不理性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phara, please. The jump induces psychosis. You're not thinking straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.79,0:53:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思维没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm thinking just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.09,0:53:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准目标的能力也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also aiming.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.34,0:53:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 如果你不喜欢我接下来的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, if you don't like what I have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.55,0:54:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说完话 你可以杀了我 你可以杀死所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can kill me when I'm done. You can kill all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.39,0:54:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.89,0:54:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That ship…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.15,0:54:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们族群将取得的最强大武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is the most powerful weapon your people will ever get their hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.36,0:54:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样 为何摧毁它 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If that's the case, why destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.70,0:54:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-为何不利用它  -如何利用 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Why not use it for leverage? -How?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.37,0:54:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们团结起来 三个世界的人齐心协力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We band together, all three worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.62,0:54:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再移动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.92,0:54:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以共享无敌战舰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can share the Invictus.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.75,0:54:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以合作修好它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can repair it, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.88,0:54:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需要让理性的声音比感性更响亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All we have to do is let our logic speak louder than our emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.56,0:54:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉 停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phara, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.98,0:54:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要与你们的猎手为敌 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You would take up arms against your own Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.86,0:54:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狩猎行动结束了 法拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hunt is over, Phara.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.42,0:55:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉 停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Phara, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.82,0:55:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-瞄准 -弗里斯通 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Take aim! -Freestone, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.71,0:55:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死了 放下武器吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gone. Drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.35,0:56:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前的景象令人鼓舞啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, this is encouraging.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.44,0:56:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安纳克里昂人 狄斯比斯人和端点星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anacreons, Thespins, and Termini.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.90,0:56:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到大家齐聚在此 我看到了希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seeing you all gathered here gives me hope…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.82,0:56:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们真的能取得成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we might actually pull this off.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.84,0:57:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻译：易晗
